&lt;p>Suppose you have vast land and no one around you. &lt;br>
For you living you want to work in the field &lt;br>
and you do not have any tool, &lt;br>
any knowledge about how to dig the earth, &lt;br>
how to put seed and how crop come, &lt;br>
how to cut the crop and how to treat the field after cutting the crop &lt;br>
then what will you do?&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>